Enable Work Summaries

View Setup AND Customize Application

To use generative AI with Einstein for Service: Work Summaries, first turn on Einstein Generative AI.

From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Work Summaries, and then select Einstein Work Summaries.
Turn on Einstein Work Summaries.
